<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbde64a7b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6987"><num value="6987">§ 6987.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated not to exceed $35,000,000 for the fiscal year 1978 to carry out the purposes of this subchapter (except for <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s6982">section 6982 of this title</ref>).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbde64a7c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/272/tII/s8007">Pub. L. 89–272, title II, § 8007</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/94/580/s2">Pub. L. 94–580, § 2</ref>, <date date="1976-10-21">Oct. 21, 1976</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/90/2839">90 Stat. 2839</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbde64a7d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbde64a7e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idbde64a7f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Provisions similar to those in this section were contained in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3259">section 3259 of this title</ref>, prior to the general amendment of the Solid Waste Disposal Act by <ref href="/us/pl/94/580">Pub. L. 94–580</ref>.</p>
</note>
